com.mongodb

Class WriteResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mongodb.WriteResult

  • public class WriteResult
extends Object
    This class lets you access the results of the previous write. If the write was performed with an acknowledged write concern, this just stores the result of the write.
    See Also:
    WriteConcern.UNACKNOWLEDGED
